The remains of late former governor of Oyo State, Abiola Ajimobi, will be interred on Sunday, 28th June at his Ishaq Abiola Ajimobi Central Mosque, Oke Ado. Strict COVID-19 protocols are to be adhered in light of the current circumstances of our national health challenges. Details of a larger funeral gathering will be announced where more of his well wishers will have the opportunity to pay him their respect, the family said. See Also






